@layout MainLayout
@page "/"

<div class="page">
    <div id="homepage-header">
        <div>
            <img src="https://ourspotkc.azurewebsites.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/animation-w-alpha-channel.gif" alt="Homepage Logo" id="homepage-header__header">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row banner banner-full-width">
            <div class="col-m-3 col-sm-12">
                <h2>Our Impact</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-m-9 col-sm-12">
                While our focus is for LGBTQ+ individuals; which slightly makes us different overall, we also provide the community with intentional efforts to empower diverse intersecting identities within the LGBTQ+ community thru skill building, support and resources from all aspects of life, health and education. We pride ourselves in allowing the communities that we serve to determine the work that we are doing; not funding, in turn differentiating OSKC from mainstream organizations here in the KC metro area.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row card-row">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card" style="width: 100%; min-width: 15rem;">
                    <h2 class="card-img-top text-center">10+</h2>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Thousand Dollars Raised.</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">All money raised benefits the community through educational events and resources.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col col-sm-12">
                <div class="card" style="width: 100%; min-width: 15rem;">
                    <h2 class="card-img-top text-center">12+</h2>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Years Spent Serving Communities</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Our board is made of individuals who have spent years serving the Kansas City community.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card" style="width: 100%; min-width: 15rem;">
                    <h2 class="card-img-top text-center">15+</h2>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Thousand People Impact</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Community reach is important to us.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row banner banner-full-width">
            <div class="col-m-3 col-sm-12">
                <h2>Our Values</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-m-9 col-sm-12">
                <ul>
                    <li>We have equality and respect for all identities regardless of sexual orientation, socio-economic status, or gender.</li>
                    <li>We promote empowerment and skill enhancements.</li>
                    <li>We support by uplifting individuals to their maximum potential.</li>
                    <li>We are understanding of culturally competency within the LGBTQ+ community.</li>
                    <li>We approach our work from a C.A.R.E. perspective.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
